- \(P(\text{all three drugs have at most 8 successes}) = (0.8506916541)^3 \approx 0.615625\)
- \(P(\text{maximum successes} > 8) = 1 - 0.615625 = 0.384375\)

Rounding to three decimal places, the result is 0.384.

