\[
S \approx 0.86602540378 \times 1.0545718 \times 10^{-34} \approx 9.132855 \times 10^{-35}  \text{J} \cdot \text{s}.
\]

Expressed in units of \( 10^{-35}  \text{J} \cdot \text{s} \), the numerical value is approximately 9.132855. Rounding to three significant figures, which is reasonable given the precision of the constants, gives 9.13.

